Purpose:
~~~~~~~~
This program is a simple editor for the cars in Test Drive 1 and 4D Sports
Driving. With this program, you can change the gear ratios and acceleration
of all cars in TD1 and 4D SD.

Requirements:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This program requires v2.04 or higher of the operating system to run. To
actually have any use of it, you must have a copy of TestDrive 1 (TD1)
and/or 4D Sports Driving (4D SD).

Usage:
~~~~~~
This program can be started from both Workbench and CLI. Double-click on
its icon to start it from Workbench. To start it from CLI, you must enter
the full path and the name of the editor (TDCarEd) and press return. If
you are going to change the cars for 4D SD, you may change the current dir
to the one that contains the game. This makes it easier to find the car
data files. Test Drive 1 uses an absolute path for its files, because it
isn't programmed to be installed on a hard drive.

