Some things to try (Test Drive 1):
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    All cars:

    Set max rpm to 32766 (max) and leave everything else. This will make
    the engine impossible to burn. For best effect, pull the joystick
    forward in about 5 seconds before start driving. To make the car go
    faster, without changing the gear ratios, shift the gear one step back
    at a high speed, and continue to drive.

    Acceleration curve:

    Change to whatever you want. The acceleration for TD1 is less sensitive
    than it is for 4D SD.

    Lotus:
        Gears:      65523, 34392, 17330, 8124, 3248

